11#ifndef RTC_BASE_EXPERIMENTS_JITTER_UPPER_BOUND_EXPERIMENT_H_
12#define RTC_BASE_EXPERIMENTS_JITTER_UPPER_BOUND_EXPERIMENT_H_
13
14#include "absl/types/optional.h"
15
16namespace webrtc {
17
18class JitterUpperBoundExperiment {
19 public:
20 // Returns nullopt if experiment is not on, otherwise returns the configured
21 // upper bound for frame delay delta used in jitter estimation, expressed as
22 // number of standard deviations of the current deviation from the expected
23 // delay.
24 static absl::optional<double> GetUpperBoundSigmas();
25
26 static const char kJitterUpperBoundExperimentName[];
27};
28
29} // namespace webrtc

31#endif // RTC_BASE_EXPERIMENTS_JITTER_UPPER_BOUND_EXPERIMENT_H_
